<div class="language-bash line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="prismjs" data-ext="sh"><pre v-pre><code><span class="line"><span class="token function">ping</span> www.baidu.com <span class="token parameter variable">-c</span> <span class="token number">3</span></span>
